---
title: "US46 — Manage expertise categories"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ExpertProfileScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>UpdateExpertProfile
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ExpertProfile · ExpertCategory
  A->>B: pick specialty categories, tap SAVE
  B->>C: saveCategories(categoryIds)
  C->>E: setExpertCategories(expertId, categoryIds)
  alt saved
    E-->>C: ExpertCategory rows (linked)
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (saved)
    B-->>A: appears under those categories in Experts tab
  else save failed
    E-->>C: PostgrestException
    C-->>B: state = AsyncError
    B-->>A: "Could not update categories. Try again."
  end
  note over E: setExpertCategories via SupabaseGateway → expert_categories (RLS).<br/>master category list owned by admin (US58)
